---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Who We Work With | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management works with sophisticated individuals and organisations who operate across borders and require an advisor who understands the full picture of their international business."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573164713714-d95e436ab8d6?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Clients</span>
      <h1>Who We Work With</h1>
      <p>Sophisticated clients who operate across borders.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">The Clients We Serve</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Not Every Client. The Right Clients.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management does not serve every type of client. We work with a defined group of sophisticated individuals and organisations who share a common characteristic: they operate across borders and require an advisor who understands the full picture of their international business — not just a single jurisdiction or a single service line.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">We are selective about the mandates we accept. Before any engagement begins, we assess honestly whether we can add meaningful value. If we cannot, we say so. This approach allows us to maintain the quality of advice and depth of senior attention that our existing clients depend on.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Who We Advise</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">The Profiles We Work With</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>International Entrepreneurs</h3>
          <p>Founders building businesses across multiple jurisdictions — from initial market entry and entity formation through to complex multi-entity group structures, payroll, and ongoing compliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Private Investors &amp; Family Offices</h3>
          <p>Private capital deploying across international markets — structuring investment vehicles, managing cross-border tax efficiency, and navigating regulatory requirements in target jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Multinational Corporations</h3>
          <p>Established businesses expanding into new markets or rationalising complex international structures — requiring experienced advisory that coordinates legal, tax, and regulatory requirements across jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>High-Net-Worth Individuals</h3>
          <p>Internationally mobile individuals requiring residence planning, UAE Golden Visa and EU residency programmes, citizenship advisory, and coordination of cross-border personal tax obligations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Web3 &amp; Crypto Businesses</h3>
          <p>Exchanges, protocols, token issuers, and Web3 infrastructure businesses requiring VARA, MiCA, MAS, and other regulatory licensing, plus entity formation and AML programme design.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Professional Service Firms</h3>
          <p>Law firms, accounting practices, and consultancies seeking to extend their international offering through a coordinated referral relationship with an established cross-border advisory.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">Our Standard</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">What Our Clients Expect From Us.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78)">Every ARM Management client receives the same standard of service regardless of mandate size: a named senior advisor who knows their business, honest assessments before work begins, fixed and transparent fees, and complete confidentiality. We do not pass clients to junior associates after onboarding. We do not accept mandates where we cannot genuinely add value. And we do not maintain client relationships that have drifted beyond our core competencies.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Complete Confidentiality</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">All client information is handled with absolute discretion. We do not publish client names, case studies, or transaction details without explicit written permission.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Senior Continuity</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">The advisor who assesses your situation is the advisor who manages it. No handoffs, no account managers, no junior associates handling your most important matters.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Honest Assessments</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We tell clients honestly when something will not work, when a timeline is unrealistic, or when a jurisdiction presents risks that outweigh the commercial benefit. We have declined mandates. Our clients value that.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.3);padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;margin-bottom:10px">Transparent Fees</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Every engagement is scoped and priced before work begins. No hourly billing surprises. No scope creep billed without discussion. Fees reflect value delivered, not time spent.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Schedule a Consultation</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Every new client engagement begins with a confidential introductory conversation. Tell us about your situation and what you are trying to achieve. We will tell you honestly whether and how we can help.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
